The so-called university spirit refers to a series of ideas and value pursuits that a university has accumulated over a long period of time during its development. It is the soul of a university.
From ancient times to the present, the spirit of university has been essential to the development of politics, economy, culture, science and technology, society, and even the progress of a nation.
Since the birth of the world's first university in the modern sense, the university has shouldered a unique mission different from other social organizations. For universities in China, it emerged in the fall of national distress, and its spirit is deeply influenced by traditional culture and the changing times, advocating the value concept of “Ming De Ji Shi, repairing the peace” and the patriotism of “developing a strong country”.
Currently, the trend of informatization and internationalization of higher education is becoming more and more obvious. Global competition in education, science and technology, and talent continues to intensify. As an important “supply side”, the structural reform of higher education is facing unprecedented opportunities and challenges.
In particular, the proposal of the “Overall Plan for Coordinated Promotion of the Construction of World-Class Universities and First-Class Disciplines”, while demonstrating China's confidence and determination to move from a major country with higher education to a higher education power, also places higher and newer requirements on university development.
How can we strive to rank among the most popular in the world in a relatively short period of time, accelerate the construction of a number of world-class universities and a number of world-class disciplines on the basis that there is still a certain gap, and achieve “overtaking cars in corners”?
In addition to firm goal self-confidence, self-confidence in path, and self-confidence in ability, colleges and universities should also give full play to three advantages: first, latecomer advantages, through the continuous introduction of outstanding overseas academic talents, learning and drawing on the advanced experience of world-class universities, to achieve significant improvement in academic level and quality of running schools; second, cultural advantages, inheriting the wisdom connotation accumulated by Chinese civilization in 5,000 years, and promoting and developing excellent traditional culture, so as to unite strength. Shaping the brand and enhancing the image; the third is to give full play to the institutional superiority of socialist countries, strengthen goal-driven, gather consensus and joint efforts, optimize resource allocation, and provide a sustainable and solid guarantee for schools to accelerate catching up with the world's advanced level.
In particular, it is important to realize that building a world-class university cannot be one of a thousand schools. While giving full play to its advantages, each school must show its individuality and characteristics.
The characteristics of running schools should not only have common Chinese characteristics, but also reflect their unique goal positioning, school traditions, and resource endowments.
As far as Zhejiang University is concerned, we focus on highlighting the characteristics of three aspects in running schools: one is to highlight the characteristics of innovative and entrepreneurial talent training, and to build an integrated and nurturing environment integrating science and education and school-enterprise to form a full-chain entrepreneurship education ecosystem; second, highlighting the characteristics of cross-disciplinary convergence, promoting the optimization and adjustment of the discipline system, creating an institutional environment where disciplines intersect, and actively cultivating cross-cutting emerging disciplines and iconic intersecting achievements; third, Highlight the characteristics of the school running system and social services, carry out in-depth international exchanges and cooperation, and accelerate the formation of an industry-university-research cooperation system at Pan-Zhejiang University.
In this process, it is particularly important to always adhere to the university spirit so that the university spirit and the zeitgeist resonate with the spirit of the times at the same frequency.
For Zhejiang University, the school motto of “seeking truth and innovation”, the common values of “studying diligently, practicing morality, discerning, and being truthful” and “the Haina River, enlightening the truth and virtue, opening things up to the people before us, and building our country” together form the latest expression system of the spirit of Zhejiang University.
This is an important guarantee for schools to adhere to the correct direction of running schools, continuously accumulate cultural heights, and gather spiritual strength. It has rich connotations and far-reaching significance.
Among them, “Haina River” emphasizes the spirit of openness and inclusiveness, reflecting the mind of “the world's talents for my use”, and manifests itself in drawing on the high-quality concept of world-famous schools to run schools and educate people; “enlightenment and virtue” emphasizes the spirit of seeking truth and the best spirit of kindness, which means that universities are more motivated by virtue and personality while pursuing truth; “opening things before people” embodies the spirit of reform and innovation, including The search for new knowledge and innovation in scientific research also manifests itself in reform and development, revolutionizing the past; “Shoring Our State” emphasizes patriotism and dedication, and says that universities should always share common honor and humiliation with the destiny of the nation.
This series of spiritual ideas and value pursuits is the soul of Zhejiang University's 120-year run school.
“The wise hear silently, and the wise see the invisible”.
Chinese colleges and universities should further build on the overall cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics, deeply grasp the direction of the times and historical mission in which higher education undertakings are located, and accelerate their construction into world-class universities.
At the same time, adhering to humanistic care and independence and freedom, let the spirit of the university stir up each other with the spirit of the times and the national spirit, thus providing inexhaustible impetus for the realization of the prosperity and strength of the country and the revitalization of the nation, and the realization of the common ideals
